OL,3,CCompanies fined after two men crushed
OL,4,Cto death
OL,6,FThe two men had been working from a
OL,7,Fnearby mobile platform and were still
OL,8,Finside when the racking tipped onto
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,FMr Horton and Mr Pickstock suffered
OL,12,Ffatal injuries and died shortly after
OL,13,Fthe incident on 29 October 2020.
OL,15,FThe HSE said the racking was being
OL,16,Ftested at a site belonging to Space
OL,17,FProductiv Ltd, where Mr Horton, from
OL,18,FIlkley, was managing director.
