OL,3,CCompanies fined after two men crushed
OL,4,Cto death
OL,6,FMr Pickstock, who was from Chorley,
OL,7,Fwas self-employed and working for a
OL,8,Fcompany called Collins Site Services.
OL,10,FThe HSE said both companies failed to
OL,11,Fassess the risks they faced, including
OL,12,Fthat the pair were within the collapse
OL,13,Fzone of the racking during testing.
OL,15,FSpace Productiv Ltd was fined #97,500
OL,16,Fand ordered to pay #17,377 in costs at
OL,17,FLeeds Crown Court.
OL,19,FCollins Site Services Ltd was fined
OL,20,F#60,000 and ordered to pay #10,292 in
OL,21,Fcosts.
