OL,6,FIn a statement Mr Pickstock's son Jack
OL,7,FStileman said he was "a hard worker
OL,8,Fand content in his life".
OL,10,FHe added: "He didn't like unnecessary
OL,11,Fdrama or unkindness, and he was
OL,12,Fgrateful for what he had.
OL,14,F"My future children do not get the
OL,15,Fchance to have a grandfather. I feel
OL,16,Fheartbroken for them that the
OL,17,Fcircumstances surrounding my dad's
OL,18,Fdeath happened at work and could very
OL,19,Fpossibly have been avoided."
