OL,6,FMr Horton's daughter Emma said: "There
OL,7,Fare no words that can fully capture
OL,8,Fthe magnitude of our loss.
OL,10,F"His humour, warmth and generosity are
OL,11,Fdeeply missed by all who knew him."
OL,13,FHSE Inspector Mark Slater said: "In
OL,14,Fthis case, inadequate planning and
OL,15,Funsafe systems of work exposed workers
OL,16,Fto an unacceptable level of risk. This
OL,17,Fwas a wholly avoidable incident."
